asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Duck Season
description:
In a land where rabbits have taken over as the Alpha race... the ducks have found themselves in hiding. As the winds shift and a light breeze comes over the horizon, one thing is crystal clear....It's Duck season. And the Fluf World.... is on the hunt.

It was opening day, and the early bird gets the worm. Or so they say. Wallace was up all night with the crew in his luxury High Roller Burrow. All the hottest Apes and Flufs were there. No one was bored. Wallace threw on his camo jacket and headed out the door, Cigar in his mouth, as always, and his SX4 20-Guage leaning on his shoulder. "Today is gonna be a good day."

He hopped in his Lambo and headed over to his buddy Snoops to link up for the hunt. But they never quite made it out of Snoops crib. They got lost in time, tearing up a studio session they started on the fly. Mr. E was laying down sick beats and Snoop was tearing it up on the mic. Before you know it they had put together a sick track and one of the Party Bears got it all on camera. After a little editing, it was online and going viral. 

Huh, I spose they will go Duck Hunting tomorrow. Hard to stay on a single path when you have the whole Underground to keep things live.

.....to be continued.

name: Bunny Binion
description: Lester Bunny Binion aka "Lucky Sevens" is an American gambling icon, career criminal, and convicted murderer who established illegal gambling operations in the Dallas-Fur Worth, Texas area. After relocating to Cotton-Tail Nevada, where gambling was legal, Binion opened the successful Bunny Binion's Horseshoe casino in downtown Las Vegans. After dozens of run-in's with the Fuzz, and a painful case of rabbits foot, Binion had no choice but hang up the cards and go into hiding. Some would say his disappearance marked the end of an era. Others rejoiced at their newfound freedom. But to this day, thousands of Flufs still gather annually to honor Binion, and battle it out,  at the Fluf Series of Poker. To say there aren't murmurs of when the former FSOP champ will return to claim his crown would be a foolish statement.  And although Lester and his burrow have yet to be uncovered, legend says that he still alive...patiently hoping, and hopping, for the right moment to reclaim his title as the Greatest Organized Crime Lord in all of Fluf World.
